        <num>CCP 4302</num>
        <heading>4302.  Terms of sale</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4302.  Terms of sale
A sale of minor's property shall be for cash, unless upon the petition of the tutor the court authorizes a credit sale.  When a credit sale is authorized, the order shall specify the terms of the sale and the security.</p>
        </content>
